Welcome to Nexmo.
Making = your first API call is easy

Hi Ashutosh,

You're in = good company. Thousands of other developers already use Nexmo everyday = for their cloud communications applications. Here are some useful = resources to get you started with Nexmo.

Next steps
You'll be making your first = API call in no time...

  • Grab your API key and = secret in the Dashboard
  • Send yourself = an SMS, WhatsApp, 2FA PIN = code, or make your first phone = call with our interactive demos
  • Browse = the Nexmo = Developer Centre for documentation, sample code, and = tutorials
  • Check out our open source libraries and tools on = Github
  • Get help and = support through our knowledge base

Not a developer?
No = problem, invite your = team to help you get up and running.

Custom pricing and switching service
For= high volume customers we can customise pricing plans and tailor your = account features to meet your business requirements. Nexmo also provides = a moving service to help you switch from another service.

If you would like to find out more, contact = sales

Regards,
The Nexmo Team

Nexmo, Vonage API Platform, 501 2nd = Street, Suite 310 San Francisco, CA 94107
